                            <p>123 Main Street, Gulberg III, Lahore, Pakistan</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/000000/phone.png" alt="Phone">
                        <div>
                            <h4>Phone Number</h4>
                            <p>+92 300 1234567</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/000000/email.png" alt="Email">
                        <div>
                            <h4>Email Address</h4>
                            <p>support@workerfinder.pk</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/000000/clock.png" alt="Hours">
                        <div>
                            <h4>Working Hours</h4>
                            <p>Monday - Saturday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-form">
                    <h3>Send us a Message</h3>
                    <form>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Your Full Name" required>
                        <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email Address" required>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Subject">
                        <textarea placeholder="Write your message here..." rows="5" required></textarea>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
    <section class="faq" id="faq">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Find answers to common questions about WorkerFinder</p>

            <div class="faq-container">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>How do I create an account on WorkerFinder?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Creating an account is simple and free. Click on the "Signup" button in the navigation bar, fill in your basic information including name, email, and phone number. You can register as a client looking to hire workers or as a worker offering your services. After registration, verify your email address to activate your account.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>How are workers verified on the platform?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>All workers on WorkerFinder go through a verification process. This includes ID verification using CNIC, skill assessment based on their experience and certifications, and background checks. Workers with completed verifications display a verified badge on their profile, giving you confidence in their authenticity.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>What payment methods are accepted?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>WorkerFinder supports multiple payment methods for your convenience. You can pay using bank transfer, JazzCash, EasyPaisa, or cash on completion. All online payments are processed through secure payment gateways to ensure your financial information remains protected.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>Can I cancel a job after posting it?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, you can cancel a job posting at any time before hiring a worker. If you have already hired a worker and need to cancel, please communicate with the worker through our messaging system. Cancellation policies may vary depending on whether work has already begun. We recommend discussing any changes directly with the hired worker.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>How do I contact a worker before hiring?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Once you post a job and receive applications, you can view each worker's profile and use our built-in messaging system to communicate with them. This allows you to discuss job details, negotiate pricing, and ask questions before making your hiring decision. All conversations are saved in your account for reference.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>What if I am not satisfied with the work?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Customer satisfaction is our priority. If you are not satisfied with the work, first try to resolve the issue directly with the worker. If that does not work, you can file a complaint through our support system. Our team will review the case and help mediate a fair resolution. We also have a review system where you can rate workers based on their performance.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

